{
  "id": "6a03e9dd0629fe1c7d6ef68c",
  "title": "不満は「え～」",
  "created": 1778641375,
  "updated": 1778641390,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a03e9dd0629fe1c7d6ef68c",
      "text": "不満は「え～」",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddef5",
      "text": "from [2026/04/08]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddef6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641378
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddef7",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddef8",
      "text": " [\" え〜[caki.icon]]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddef9",
      "text": "\t「え～」というのは、とても優れた感情表現だと思う。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddefa",
      "text": "\t相手に対するちょっとした不満やザワツキのようなものを[詳細に言語化]せずに、可愛い程度に表現できる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddefb",
      "text": "\t\t言語化はすればするほど余計にツッコミどころが生まれるから、核となる部分だけを端的に発せられればそれでもう良いのだと思う。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddefc",
      "text": "\t[そうか？]を辞めて[え〜]と言うようにします[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddefd",
      "text": "\t\t[お茶.icon][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddefe",
      "text": "\t\tにゅ〜[mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddeff",
      "text": "\t[ふぇぇ]もありますよ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddf00",
      "text": "\t\tふぇぇ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9de00000000001ddf01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641375,
      "updated": 1778641375
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9e400000000001ddf02",
      "text": "違うやつ：[はえ〜]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641381,
      "updated": 1778641390
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e9e600000000001ddf03",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778641382,
      "updated": 1778641382
    }
  ]
}